# Admin — Batches

### List batches
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###

### Create batch
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "batch_name": "Initial batch",
  "quantity": 10,
  "max_devices": 1,
  "code_prefix": "TV",
  "notes": "First batch for testing"
}

###

### Read batch detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/batches/{{batchId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}

###